markdownRemark.html: An important new collection of essays on printer's marks is: Anja Wolkenhauer, and Bernhard F. Scholtz, eds. Typographorum Emblemata. The Printer's Mark in the Context of Early Modern Culture, Berlin and Boston, Walter de Gruyter, 2018. I will cite this volume repeatedly in the comments that follow in this chapter, using the shorthand Typographorum Emblemata and page numbers.
